Package: sore
Type: Package
Title: Annotation-Ranked Bayesian Fine-Mapping of GWAS Signals
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Siyi", "Chen",
                  email = "sche11@lsuhsc.edu",
                  role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R implementation of the SoRE (Sum of Ranked Effects) prior
    and the V-SoRE empirical-Bayes reweighting algorithm for fine-mapping
    GWAS summary statistics. V-SoRE wraps SuSiE-RSS as an inner solver and
    drives an outer reweighting loop based on the agreement between
    annotation ranks and current posterior inclusion probabilities. See
    Chen (2026), Annotation-Ranked Bayesian Fine-Mapping of GWAS Signals
    with Data-Adaptive Reversion to Exchangeability.
